title: Haiti Port Au Prince Land Use Data from United Nation MINUSTAH
name: Haiti Port Au Prince Land Use Data from United Nation MINUSTAH
description: This data was released 1/16/10 from the United Nations Stabilization Mission in Haiti (MINUSTAH).  The data layer shows land use for select parcels in the Port Au Prince Haiti - including industrial areas, shanty towns and green areas.
